<h3>Design-Aware Content Creation</h3>
<p>Here is where WordPress AI agents get interesting. The agent reads your theme, understands your colors, fonts, spacing, and block patterns. When it builds a page or post, the output matches your site design.</p>
<p>This eliminates the formatting gap that plagues most <a href="/blog/automated-content-creation/">automated content creation</a> workflows. You do not need to fix styling after every generated post.</p>
