<h3>Security and Permissions</h3>
<p>WordPress enforces its standard permission roles on AI agents. An agent with editor access cannot change site settings. An agent with author access cannot delete other users' posts.</p>
<p>You can also toggle individual operations on or off. Want the agent to draft posts but not publish them? That is a single setting. Every change appears in your Activity Log for full audit trails.</p>
